name: Alejandro Torres
profile_summary: The user is a 32-year-old straight man, who adheres to He/Him/His pronouns. Standing 6'1" tall, he belongs to the Hispanic/Latino ethnic group. Professionally, he works as a Civil Engineer in the engineering industry and holds a graduate degree from the University of California. Bilingual in English and Spanish, he loves immersing himself in soccer, cooking, reading, and traveling. As a Catholic, he values family, hard work, and honesty and leans toward moderate political viewpoints. He doesn't have children but looks forward to having them in the future. Currently, he practices monogamy and long-term dating. His lifestyle habits include not using drugs or marijuana, abstaining from smoking, moderate drinking, and maintaining active physical exercise. His friendly companion is a dog.
